/td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Values</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Value\" title=\"Value\">Value</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">14 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/High_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"High Level Alchemy\">High alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">8 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Low_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"Low Level Alchemy\">Low alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">5 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">Weight</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0.3 kg</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Item ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">hist21798</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Demon%27s_heart_(balance)_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Demon&#39;s heart (balance) detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Demon%27s_heart_%28balance%29_detail.png/180px-Demon%27s_heart_%28balance%29_detail.png?f45f5\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"126\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Demon%27s_heart_%28balance%29_detail.png/270px-Demon%27s_heart_%28balance%29_detail.png?f45f5 1.5x, /images/thumb/Demon%27s_heart_%28balance%29_detail.png/360px-Demon%27s_heart_%28balance%29_detail.png?f45f5 2x\" data-file-width=\"1378\" data-file-height=\"965\" /></a></div>\n<p>A <b>demon's heart</b> was a drop from the <a href=\"/w/Demon_of_Balance\" title=\"Demon of Balance\">Demon of Balance</a>. This heart, along with the hearts of <a href=\"/w/Demon%27s_heart_(light)\" title=\"Demon&#39;s heart (light)\">light</a> and <a href=\"/w/Demon%27s_heart_(darkness)\" title=\"Demon&#39;s heart (darkness)\">darkness</a> from the <a href=\"/w/Demon_of_Light\" title=\"Demon of Light\">Demon of Light</a> and <a href=\"/w/Demon_of_Darkness\" title=\"Demon of Darkness\">Demon of Darkness</a> respectively, was required to imbue a <a href=\"/w/God_cape\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God cape\">god cape</a> during the <a href=\"/w/Mage_Arena_II\" title=\"Mage Arena II\">Mage Arena II</a> <a href=\"/w/Miniquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Miniquest\">miniquest</a>.\n</p><p>Subsequent imbues would require only one heart of the player's choice, in which this heart would imbue a <a href=\"/w/Guthix_cape\" title=\"Guthix cape\">Guthix cape</a> into an <a href=\"/w/Imbued_guthix_cape\" title=\"Imbued guthix cape\">Imbued guthix cape</a>.\n</p><p>The demon's heart could not be deposited into a <a href=\"/w/Bank\" title=\"Bank\">bank</a>, and was <b>always</b> lost upon death, so it was recommended to turn it in to <a href=\"/w/Kolodion\" title=\"Kolodion\">Kolodion</a> as soon as possible.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Item_sources\">Item sources</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Demon%27s_heart_(balance)?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Item sources\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Demon%27s_heart_(balance)?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Item sources\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"seealso\">For an exhaustive list of all known sources for this item, see <span class=\"plainlinks\"><a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Special:Ask?limit=500&amp;p%5Bformat%5D=table&amp;p%5Bmainlabel%5D=Monster&amp;po=%3FDrop+Quantity%0A%3FRarity&amp;q=%5B%5BDropped+item%3A%3ADemon%27s+heart+%28balance%29%5D%5D\">here</a></span> (<span class=\"plainlinks\